Enum FieldExtendedPropertyType

public enum FieldExtendedPropertyType
extends Enum<FieldExtendedPropertyType>

The enum that represents the field extended property. Some of them are valid only with certain FieldType.

Used to create a FieldExtendedProperty

Since:
1.0
Author:
Giancarlo Parma

Enum Constant Detail

DECIMAL_FORMAT

public static final FieldExtendedPropertyType DECIMAL_FORMAT
Used to get control of the formatting of a numeric field.

It's valid only when the field is of type FieldType.N. The value must be a java.text.DecimalFormat

REMOVE_DECIMAL_SEPARATOR

public static final FieldExtendedPropertyType REMOVE_DECIMAL_SEPARATOR
Used to remove decimal separator on the formatting of a numeric field.

It's valid only when the field is of type FieldType.N and the FieldExtendedPropertyType.DECIMAL_FORMAT is used. The value must be a java.lang.Boolean

DATE_FORMAT

public static final FieldExtendedPropertyType DATE_FORMAT
Used to get control of the formatting of a alphanumeric field when the field represents a date.

It's valid only when the field is of type FieldType.AN and the FieldExtendedPropertyType.BOOLEAN_FORMAT is not used and the FieldExtendedPropertyType.CUSTOM_FORMAT is not used. The value must be a java.text.DateFormat

BOOLEAN_FORMAT

public static final FieldExtendedPropertyType BOOLEAN_FORMAT
Used to get control of the formatting of a alphanumeric field when the field represents a boolean.

It's valid only when the field is of type FieldType.AN and the FieldExtendedPropertyType.DATE_FORMAT is not used and the FieldExtendedPropertyType.CUSTOM_FORMAT is not used. The value must be a org.fixefid.record.format.BooleanFormat

CUSTOM_FORMAT

public static final FieldExtendedPropertyType CUSTOM_FORMAT
Used to get control of the formatting of a alphanumeric field when the field represents a string.

It's valid only when the field is of type FieldType.AN and the FieldExtendedPropertyType.DATE_FORMAT is not used and the FieldExtendedPropertyType.BOOLEAN_FORMAT is not used. The value must be a org.fixefid.record.format.CustomFormat

LPAD

public static final FieldExtendedPropertyType LPAD
Used to get control of the field padding. The LPAD force the left padding with the value provided with the FieldExtendedProperty

RPAD

public static final FieldExtendedPropertyType RPAD
Used to get control of the field padding. The LPAD force the right padding with the value provided with the FieldExtendedProperty

VALIDATOR

public static final FieldExtendedPropertyType VALIDATOR
Used to get control of the field validation. The value must be a org.fixefid.record.field.FieldValidator
